27
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:29,629
SPEAKER_31: They're too tired. Been at it all night.

42
00:05:38,129 --> 00:05:39,459
SPEAKER_31: Take care.

43
00:05:40,259 --> 00:05:42,319
SPEAKER_31: Take care, Master.

131
00:14:10,409 --> 00:14:12,710
SPEAKER_31: Master Fugui, I'm sorry...

132
00:14:12,779 --> 00:14:15,769
SPEAKER_31: but you've nothing left.
What would you wager?

133
00:14:16,110 --> 00:14:18,809
SPEAKER_31: If you're unhappy, talk to Mr. Xie.

145
00:15:00,620 --> 00:15:03,120
SPEAKER_31: Not that we'd accept it as ante.

183
00:19:32,059 --> 00:19:36,660
SPEAKER_31: It's valuable. Don't scratch it. Take it slowly.

228
00:24:09,470 --> 00:24:11,769
SPEAKER_31: This old home of yours is great.

229
00:24:12,180 --> 00:24:14,369
SPEAKER_31: Warm in winter, cool in summer.

289
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:45,220
SPEAKER_31: The wounded who froze to death.

290
00:32:46,019 --> 00:32:49,420
SPEAKER_31: Put it on. We must survive.

631
01:13:07,039 --> 01:13:08,670
SPEAKER_31: It's Fugui's son?

632
01:13:09,750 --> 01:13:11,649
SPEAKER_31: District Chief arrived after dark.

633
01:13:11,710 --> 01:13:16,079
SPEAKER_31: He backed up,
and his jeep knocked the wall down.

634
01:13:16,149 --> 01:13:19,020
SPEAKER_31: Youqing was sleeping on the other side.

635
01:13:19,560 --> 01:13:21,850
SPEAKER_31: When the wall collapsed...

636
01:13:22,329 --> 01:13:24,159
SPEAKER_31: he didn't have a chance.

637
01:13:24,229 --> 01:13:26,560
SPEAKER_31: The District Chief was hurt, too.

638
01:13:27,800 --> 01:13:30,130
SPEAKER_31: He hadn't slept for three days.

639
01:13:56,729 --> 01:13:58,420
SPEAKER_31: Fugui, listen to me.

640
01:13:58,489 --> 01:14:02,430
SPEAKER_31: We have to try and bear it,
even in the worst of times.

822
01:31:36,520 --> 01:31:38,449
SPEAKER_31: We must be going.

829
01:32:01,979 --> 01:32:04,810
SPEAKER_31: Thanks, we'll go to the factory bathhouse.

830
01:32:10,619 --> 01:32:12,920
SPEAKER_31: You've gone to so much trouble.

831
01:32:13,119 --> 01:32:14,779
SPEAKER_31: Please come again.

832
01:32:22,359 --> 01:32:25,489
SPEAKER_31: What do you think about Fengxia and me?

867
01:36:35,119 --> 01:36:36,479
SPEAKER_31: Dad, Mom...

1058
01:51:42,520 --> 01:51:44,550
SPEAKER_31: They've been locked away.

1059
01:51:44,930 --> 01:51:48,020
SPEAKER_31: The Red Guards are in control!

1077
01:53:27,560 --> 01:53:29,359
SPEAKER_31: How vile can you get?

1145
01:58:59,689 --> 01:59:02,989
SPEAKER_31: Dad! Mom! Has she given birth?

1148
01:59:07,970 --> 01:59:09,590
SPEAKER_31: Do you hear him?

1149
01:59:09,670 --> 01:59:11,329
SPEAKER_31: Are they in there?

1150
01:59:11,869 --> 01:59:13,460
SPEAKER_31: - Have a look.
- Not yet!

1151
01:59:13,539 --> 01:59:15,529
SPEAKER_31: Please, I'm the father!

1155
01:59:28,289 --> 01:59:29,720
SPEAKER_31: Is it a boy?

1156
01:59:30,659 --> 01:59:32,279
SPEAKER_31: Yes, 7.9 pounds!

1181
02:01:34,449 --> 02:01:36,810
SPEAKER_31: Don't panic. Think of something.

